title: Act2_EveMeeting_N9
---
/// no repeat
<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: Oh, Cyrus! Didn’t think you’d be back this fast.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Has anything happened yet?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: Uh... no?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: That’s good to hear. I’ll get going then.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: Wait. Where are you going? With all your gear?
Eve: I’m your dispatcher. If this has something to do with the monsters, you should let me know. It’s too risky to go out on your own.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: You don’t understand. Just stay here and you’ll be safe.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: ...There seems to be something you're not telling me. But you’ve always been mysterious.
Eve: Either way, let me come with you. Don’t go off on your own.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: I’m sorry. This is to save everyone. What happens to me is unimportant. True justice means to save the majority, even if sacrifice is needed.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: But you’re part of “everyone,” Cyrus. Whatever you aren’t telling me... I know it is dangerous. 
Eve: Don’t you realize someone might be upset if you get hurt?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: ...Sorry.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Eve>>
Eve: Hey! You-
Eve: ...And he’s fast.

<<spawn_enemies YarnManager>>
<<jump Back_To_Game>>
===


