title: Act2_LunaIntro_Boss_PostCombat
---
<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: ...Tch. I came prepared, but I still can’t beat it. Is there no other way?
Cyrus: !

<<set_portrait YarnManager Police>>
???:  Hey—! You still breathing?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Who are—?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Police>>
Police: We’re the police dept.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: ...So my call went through.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Police>>
Police: You a hunter? Good work holding it in place. Captain Luna will finish it.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Luna>>
Luna: ...Hah, what a nasty looking thing.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: Their captain is truly powerful... She’s handling it all on her own.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Police>>
Officer 1: Huh, if you think about it, it’s pretty smart. The mayor would never be near a memory monster. No wonder we never caught him. We’d never know that he wouldn't be attacked.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: ...“Never be near”? What do you mean?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Police>>
Officer 1: Memory monsters don’t go after false humans. They’re drawn to real people. That’s why I’m saying I’m not against those “witch hunt” rituals.

<<clear_portrait YarnManager>>
Memory Monster: RRRRAAAAA—

<<set_portrait YarnManager Luna>>
Luna: How crude. I’ve spent too long on you. Goodbye.
: [i]stab[/i]

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: ...It’s actually dead.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Luna>>
Luna: Start the cleanup.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Police>>
Officer 1: Yes, captain!

<<set_portrait YarnManager Luna>>
Luna: ...You.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: ?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Luna>>
Luna: ...Heh.
Luna: Hahahahhahahahha!

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: What are you—?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Luna>>
Luna: I can’t believe you’d have the audacity to show up here.

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: ...Do we know each oth—?!

: [i]Insert fight[/i] /// checking if there's an actual fight heres

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: I... I got stabbed?
Cyrus: Why...?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Police>>
Officer 2: AHHHHH—!

<<set_portrait YarnManager TownNPC1>>
Townspeople: Monsters—!

<<set_portrait YarnManager Luna>>
Luna: ...No.
Luna: What—? The Assimilation… is starting again?
Luna: But you’re—

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: I... thought it was... over...

<<set_portrait YarnManager Luna>>
Luna: Another false human…?

<<set_portrait YarnManager Cyrus>>
Cyrus: I’ve lost too much blood.

<<complete_room YarnManager>>
<<jump Back_To_Game>>
===